WRITING.TITLE: Looking for Musicians to play Pokmon theme.
WRITING.TEXT:
Hi all. I am after a few musicians to play the pokemon theme music at a meetup in Sydney Australia in Hyde park on the 27th July.
I know this is short notice but I didn't think that my event would get as much attention as it did. I just wanted to meet some people from the other teams, compare pokemons and have a laugh at some crazy catching stories that I am sure people have.
Let me know if you know anyone. PM deets. Cheers

WRITING.TEXT: Hey mate. My girlfriend and I went on an all day bike trip and randomly met others doing similar while catching pokemon. It was great. I've had great experiences so far with people playing around me.
Just drained my battry there. Are you near the train station with the 3 lures? THIS IS THE PLACE TO BE!

WRITING.TITLE: Hi Sydney, I need your help.
WRITING.TEXT:
I am in need of a good councelor. I have been in sydney for a few years now and the city is getting to me in a few ways. My gp diagnosed me with depression.
I have been here before mentally and just need someone professional to talk to.
I would prefer a man as I feel it is easier to relate. If you know of someone around the city you could recommend that would be really appreciated. Please pm me the details.
Thanks for being an awesome community all.
Fucking nice mate. I give it 5/5 drop bears.
Haahhahahaha. Best response to that situation ever.
Yeah, this is defiantly an issue. People using drones for being creeps are going to trash the name pretty hard.
Where are you at? Where do you normally fly ?
Do you have any good photos or vids from this set up that you care to share ?
They are really coming down in price now tho. So many coming on the market.
yeah, I just got introduced to them a few months ago and am on the bandwagon something fierce now.

WRITING.TITLE: Any love in Sydney for Drones ?
WRITING.TEXT: Drone racing, drone videography and photography. I just think this new love for drone is awesome, we can get so many different angles now with cameras that were previously extremely pricey. What do you lot think ?
